title: Mangani
subTitle: Due to her appearance, a woman faces persistent challenges. Subjected to constant ridicule, she is rejected by numerous men, including her college crush.

title: Pratigyabadh
subTitle: Shankar grows up to become the right hand man of a gangster. His goal in life is to take revenge on the moneylender who left his family homeless and a truck driver who molested and killed his mother.

title: Lav Kush
subTitle: After Ram returns to Ayodhya, Sita is forced to go into exile. She gives birth to twins Lav and Kush, who later go to Ayodhya to attain blessings of Ram and recite the Ramayan.

title: Dastaan
